title: Trumpeter Ralph Alessi on Charlie Haden & the CalArts Jazz program
fulltitle: Trumpeter Ralph Alessi on Charlie Haden & the CalArts Jazz program
description: In this interview clip taped backstage at the 2014 Newport Jazz Festival, trumpeter Ralph Alessi talks about how his musical life was transformed by his experiences at the CalArts jazz program under the teaching and mentorship of noted bassist Charlie Haden.
